<p style="Normal" xid="519" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">Мы дописали </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">(@article), method:  :put. </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Переменная в скобочках </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">(@article) </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">передает id который нужен для нахождения  ресурса,  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">method :put</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">, меняет наш метод (по умолчанию </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">POST</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">) на нужный </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">PUT.  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">Если перезагрузить исходный код страницы то мы видим что  появилось дополнительнаое  поле:   </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;input name=” method” type="hidden”  value="put” </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"> /&gt; </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="516" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">   </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">Перейдем по ссылке  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">edit </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">сделаем изменения в нашей статье и засабмитим.  У нас появиться ошибка которая говорит что не создан метод </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">update . </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> Заходим в </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">articles_controller  </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">и создаем метод </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">update. </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="521" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">....</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
