<p style="Normal" xid="566" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">2) маршрут  	-- resources</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="568" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">	</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="570" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">3) контроллер</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="571" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="572" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">		-- index</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="582" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-"></c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">4)  actions	</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">-- new + create</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="579" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">		-- edit + update</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="580" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"> 		-- destroy (delete)</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="585" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="586" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">5) views</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="583" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="588" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">Добавим в наш контроллер </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">Action controller </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> метод </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">destroy</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="584" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="589" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">def destroy</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="590" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">@article = Article.find(params[:id]</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="591" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">@article.destroy</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="592" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">redirect_to articles_path</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="594" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">end</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="596" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"> </c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="597" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">Теперь перейдем в папочку </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">views/artticle</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">, откроем</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"> index.html.erb</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt"> и добавим туда к уже добавленным ссылкам </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">show | edit</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">, ссылочку </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">destroy.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="598" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="599" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:-none-; text-align:left; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:bold; line-height:1.000000; margin-bottom:0.0000in; font-size:12pt; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">&lt;p&gt;</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="601" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; dom-dir:ltr; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">    &lt;%=  link_to  ‘Show’,  article_path(article)  %&gt; |</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="604" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; dom-dir:ltr; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">    </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;%=  link_to  ‘Edit’,  edit_article_path(article)  %&gt;</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"> |</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="605" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; dom-dir:ltr; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">    </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">&lt;%=  link_to  ‘Destroy’,  article_path(article), method: :delete  %&gt;</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="603" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; dom-dir:ltr; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="602" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; dom-dir:ltr; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">&lt;/p&gt;</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="606" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; dom-dir:ltr; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="607" props="margin-top:0.0000in; margin-left:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; dom-dir:ltr; margin-bottom:0.0000in; line-height:1.000000; text-align:left; margin-right:0.0000in"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">В ссылке ‘Destroy’ мы добавили метод </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">delete</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">. Если мы откроем  исходные код страницы </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">index.html.erb</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">, </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">то мы увидим в нашей ссылке </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">data-method</c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; lang:-none-; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; font-size:12pt">.Сам браузер этот метод не знает. Обрабатывает его Rails. Когда к примеру загружается index.html.erb, у нас подгружаются сверху в теге head различные служебные файлы, в часности turbolinks.  Если перейдем по ссылке turbolinks, то мы увидим яваскрипт код который понимает нами созданный </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:bold; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">data-method </c><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; text-decoration:none; color:000000; font-size:12pt; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:-none-">и отправляет на сервер при помощи технологии ajax запрос на удаление записи.</c></p>
</section>
</abiword>
